          <msContents>
            <summary>Collection of works, including a treatise on music theory focusing on tonality as illustrated by the Pythagorean monochord and philosophers like Aristotle, Nicomachus, and Boethius; recipes and instructions for making various types of ink, stain removers, toothache remedies; a love poem in a later hand; two recipes in Italian.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="lat" otherLangs="ita">Latin, with two recipes in Italian</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Monocordium</title>
            </msItem>
